        <exercise id="eip-482" type="conceptual-questions"><problem id="eip-id1600770"><para id="import-auto-id2502272">What happens to the energy stored in a capacitor connected to a battery when a dielectric is inserted? Was work done in the process? </para></problem></exercise>
