    <exercise id="fs-id1998705" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1346384"><para id="import-auto-id952980">A <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext>65 µF</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{1"65 "mF} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> capacitor is used in conjunction with a motor. How much energy is stored in it when 119 V is applied?</para></problem></exercise>
